  • Methodendetails

    • process

      TransportDetails process(TransportDetails.Command cmd, Reference<User> processingUser) throws GetListThrowable, IllegalProcessException, ProcessingException
      method process

      Method for processing Commands requiring a User as processing User for permission management.

      Parameter:
      cmd - - Command to be processed
      processingUser - - User to be used as processing User
      Gibt zurück:
      TransportDetails - the TransportDetails that was processed
      Löst aus:
      GetListThrowable - - throwable to be thrown by GetList-Command
      IllegalProcessException - - exception to be thrown when Arguments or State are not valid for an operation
      ProcessingException - - exception to be thrown when a process fails by technical problems
